    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>By Mr. HUNTER:H.R. 777.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:The constitutional authority for the ADA Notification Actis: Section 8, Clause 1 of Article I; Section 8, Clause 18 ofArticle I.[Page H598]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
